### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Criar usuário (autenticado)
POST http://localhost:3000/user/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

{
  "name": "Maria Oliveira",
  "email": "maria@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "profession": "designer",
  "bio": "UX Designer",
  "role": "collaborator"
}

### Buscar usuário por ID (autenticado)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/replace-with-uuid
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

### Buscar usuário por email (autenticado)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/email/maria@example.com
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

### Atualizar usuário (autenticado)
PUT http://localhost:3000/user/replace-with-uuid
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token

{
  "name": "Maria Oliveira Santos",
  "bio": "Senior UX Designer"
}

### Deletar usuário (autenticado)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/user/replace-with-uuid
Authorization: Bearer replace-with-token
